description: This API takes either a ProvisonedProductId or a ProvisionedProductName, along with a list of one or more output keys, and responds with the key/value pairs of those outputs.

parameters.name: AcceptLanguage
parameters.description: The language code. jp - Japanese zh - Chinese.

parameters.name: OutputKeys
parameters.description: The list of keys that the API should return with their values. If none are provided, the API will return all outputs of the provisioned product. (string) ---

nested_items.name: Outputs
nested_items.description: Information about the product created as the result of a request. For example, the output for a CloudFormation-backed product that creates an S3 bucket would include the S3 bucket URL.

nested_items.name: NextPageToken
nested_items.description: The page token to use to retrieve the next set of results. If there are no additional results, this value is null.
